        <p>Further north along the eastern edge of the Vosges Mountains is the charming medieval village of <strong>Riquewihr</strong> with its cobblestone streets and half-timbered homes. Be sure to explore this tiny village on foot, including the <strong>Hoher Turm</strong> tower entrance on the western end of the village.</p>
